{"tid":1637051,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"下下屌人唔罷工 有冇諗過返工抗爭者幾重要","createTime":"2019-10-08T01:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:52:08.000Z","uid":83176,"like":95,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6c31719c6c483a65b63e023985760bbf8bf41889","tid":1637051,"uid":83176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:15:59.000Z","msg":"利申：幾次大罷工都有罷<br />\n<br />\n日頭返工，夜晚抗爭，星期六日用盡力發夢<br />\n已經唔知第幾個禮拜係咁，變相一星期七日冇抖過<br />\n<br />\n平時衫都唔捨得買貴（著開旺中價位）<br />\n但一見到登報課金、眾籌救人、課金星火<br />\n就將嗰日賺嘅錢一秒捐晒出去<br />\n<br />\n成日同自己 而家返工最大目標係第日爬高啲<br />\n可以請返班義士 令到佢哋唔使擔心前途<br />\n<br />\n所以求下大家唔好再屌人唔三罷<br />\n返工抗爭者都好值得大家尊敬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span>"},{"pid":"875f53f6cf2f1d609955111e33be586b11f397e6","tid":1637051,"uid":83176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:16:13.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"c8a4a5b7301830eeae4e2239df6580f57fc871be","tid":1637051,"uid":83176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:16:23.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"f8724c8c6f6133d0b4812ad40235c707c48ccb3c","tid":1637051,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:16:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa0c1bae26d358095fd141c122ca202534f56358","tid":1637051,"uid":83176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"c613092f78756281f6ae28e019d78379e31b7986","tid":1637051,"uid":83176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:16:51.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"546bcd96ce9945050cb225834a934ad2f172f441","tid":1637051,"uid":83176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"48bb13a2cf5bf9fab1f890aa700dab464f15c4ef","tid":1637051,"uid":123640,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"c